59
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:18,720
Besides, we have a good rapport

60
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,880
and I liked you from
the moment I saw you.

61
00:03:22,559 --> 00:03:23,759
Thank you for your appreciation, Mr. Yin.

62
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:24,759
It's my pleasure.

63
