85
00:04:19,719 --> 00:04:21,439
Go ahead, what is wrong with Zhao Jikai?

86
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,080
It's really about the case.

87
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:25,640
Look, Zhao Jikai and Hei

88
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,360
have been interrogated repeatedly.

89
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:30,360
And the Public Security Organs
have failed to find

90
