92
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,840
Do you know why?

93
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,520
Zhao Jikai didn't tell the whole truth.

94
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,719
Yes.

95
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:46,520
But now, I'm proud to say

96
00:04:46,599 --> 00:04:49,279
that I've got it all figured out just now.

97
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,400
What is it with you now?

98
