I don't believe any money lender
would be willing

161
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,960
to loan money to these
young people who can't repay it.

162
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,240
I thought the same as you at first.

163
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:04,279
So I deliberately
got them to filter me out

164
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:07,120
and then I borrowed 10,000 yuan
from one of them

