182
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,640
Which company do you work for?

183
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:48,999
It's none of your business.

184
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,520
Someone hired us to collect your

185
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,680
last month's debt anyway.

186
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,680
