187
00:07:54,719 --> 00:07:57,840
with interest, not a penny less.

188
00:07:58,774 --> 00:07:59,520
Mister, I...

189
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,920
I really don't have the money
at the moment.

190
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,999
You're trying to
get tough with me, right?

191
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:07,080
Listen, don't give me that.

192
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,999
It's useless.

193
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:11,120
There were many people who made excuses

194
00:08:11,159 --> 00:08:14,240
but in the end,
they had to repay the money.

195
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,960
I don't care if you are going to
ask for money from your parents,

196
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:18,520
borrow from your friends,
or beg your grandparents,

197
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,360
you have to pay back the money today.

198
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:21,840
Did you hear me?

199
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,080
Mister.

200
