the Public Security Bureau,

208
00:08:39,719 --> 00:08:40,880
you still have to pay back the money.

209
00:08:41,959 --> 00:08:42,599
You don't want to
pay back the money, right?

210
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:43,920
Undress him.

211
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,240
Mister, how about this?

212
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,120
Name a way to make money,

213
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:51,519
and I'll pay you back. I'll do anything.

214
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,079
The more you tell,
the more exciting it gets.

215
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,079
And then what did they do to you?

216
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,079
And that brings us
to the point of the story.

217
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:02,959
Ni, look.

218
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:06,079
This game,
which is the one I played a while ago,

219
00:09:06,599 --> 00:09:09,680
