220
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,719
They pay cash for the

221
00:09:11,719 --> 00:09:13,120
rare equipment and trinkets

222
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:14,839
that players get
by playing group missions.

223
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,760
These rare equipment and trinkets

224
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,719
are hard to come by

225
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,079
so they are very expensive.

226
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,519
Besides, this game also
has a treasure access restriction,

227
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:22,519
which means

228
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,880
you have a limit on the number of times
you can enter a group mission per day.

229
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:26,599
You will have to buy points in order to

230
00:09:26,599 --> 00:09:27,839
enter the group mission again.

231
00:09:28,079 --> 00:09:29,880
And, you also need an entry ticket
to enter the group mission.

232
00:09:30,599 --> 00:09:32,959
The key point is that
if you don't have good equipment

233
00:09:32,959 --> 00:09:34,079
after you enter the group mission,

234
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,079
you can't beat the monsters,

235
00:09:35,079 --> 00:09:36,399
let alone get any equipment.

236
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,800
You'll have to spend money
on equipment again.

237
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:39,680
Where can you buy the equipment?

238
00:09:39,719 --> 00:09:40,519
From Dealer.

239
00:09:40,839 --> 00:09:43,800
So it means that
whatever you do in this game,

240
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,000
you need to spend money.

241
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,639
No wonder some impulsive youngsters

242
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,479
want to buy gaming equipment

243
00:09:49,479 --> 00:09:50,599
even if they have to take out loans.

244
00:09:51,839 --> 00:09:53,320
Ni, do you remember what I said earlier?

245
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:57,000
The rare equipment and
trinkets in this game

246
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,279
are hard to come by
so they are very expensive.

247
00:09:59,599 --> 00:10:00,719
What does this tell us?

248
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,440
If you're lucky,

249
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,440
you'll get some equipment

250
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,519
in one group mission,

251
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:05,440
