252
00:10:05,479 --> 00:10:06,120
and clear your debt.

253
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,399
If you are unlucky,

254
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,399
you will not get any equipment

255
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:09,200
in a thousand group missions,

256
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,320
and you will work for nothing.

257
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,719
Well, isn't this Internet gambling
in disguise?

258
00:10:13,719 --> 00:10:14,519
Yes.

259
00:10:18,479 --> 00:10:19,120
I got it.

