00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,959
The so called Dealer is actually

261
00:10:22,079 --> 00:10:23,279
using the game equipment

262
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,120
as a virtual weight.

263
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:26,880
They are both a market maker

